  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Crime Simulator: Playgrounds</strong> is a short, hilarious, and over-the-top entry in the <strong>Crime Simulator</strong> franchise, where the goal isn’t just crime—it’s absolute mayhem. Enjoy ridiculous chaos solo or with friends, and embrace the wildest side of being a criminal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928280/extras/2ba0216aec819f884c2b19d3deb07d23.poster.avif?t=1773777936\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928280/extras/2ba0216aec819f884c2b19d3deb07d23.webm?t=1773777936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928280/extras/2ba0216aec819f884c2b19d3deb07d23.mp4?t=1773777936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have you ever wanted to <strong>throw a hammer at someone’s face</strong>? Now you can. How about <strong>pepper-spraying an entire street just for fun</strong>? Absolutely. <strong>Should a sledgehammer be so massive that it shouldn't even be legal</strong>? We got you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928280/extras/259999b1a97c2d741dd1a3a0724e3836.poster.avif?t=1773777936\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928280/extras/259999b1a97c2d741dd1a3a0724e3836.webm?t=1773777936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928280/extras/259999b1a97c2d741dd1a3a0724e3836.mp4?t=1773777936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with up to <strong>4 players</strong>, cause havoc, steal, brawl, and take over hideouts in <strong>fully open free-roam areas</strong>. Every mission is an excuse for madness—rob stores, <strong>demolish hideouts with grenade launchers</strong>, or <strong>booby-trap a rival’s getaway car with landmines</strong>. No logic, no rules—just fun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928280/extras/2d4cd9f9d49ab83702c9a9908b5deb0f.poster.avif?t=1773777936\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928280/extras/2d4cd9f9d49ab83702c9a9908b5deb0f.webm?t=1773777936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928280/extras/2d4cd9f9d49ab83702c9a9908b5deb0f.mp4?t=1773777936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Got friends?</strong> Great! <strong>Crime is better together.</strong> Work as a team, complete insane objectives and share the chaos. <strong>Voice and text chat included.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No friends?</strong> No problem! Play offline and enjoy the destruction on your own.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every fight is a playground—<strong>cops, civilians, rival gangs</strong>—everyone is a target. Grab a baseball bat, throw a crowbar at full speed, or <strong>turn an enemy into a human fireworks show</strong>.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Crime Simulator: Playgrounds</strong> is a short, hilarious, and over-the-top entry in the <strong>Crime Simulator</strong> franchise, where the goal isn’t just crime—it’s absolute mayhem. Enjoy ridiculous chaos solo or with friends, and embrace the wildest side of being a criminal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928280/extras/2ba0216aec819f884c2b19d3deb07d23.poster.avif?t=1773777936\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928280/extras/2ba0216aec819f884c2b19d3deb07d23.webm?t=1773777936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928280/extras/2ba0216aec819f884c2b19d3deb07d23.mp4?t=1773777936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have you ever wanted to <strong>throw a hammer at someone’s face</strong>? Now you can. How about <strong>pepper-spraying an entire street just for fun</strong>? Absolutely. <strong>Should a sledgehammer be so massive that it shouldn't even be legal</strong>? We got you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928280/extras/259999b1a97c2d741dd1a3a0724e3836.poster.avif?t=1773777936\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928280/extras/259999b1a97c2d741dd1a3a0724e3836.webm?t=1773777936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928280/extras/259999b1a97c2d741dd1a3a0724e3836.mp4?t=1773777936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with up to <strong>4 players</strong>, cause havoc, steal, brawl, and take over hideouts in <strong>fully open free-roam areas</strong>. Every mission is an excuse for madness—rob stores, <strong>demolish hideouts with grenade launchers</strong>, or <strong>booby-trap a rival’s getaway car with landmines</strong>. No logic, no rules—just fun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928280/extras/2d4cd9f9d49ab83702c9a9908b5deb0f.poster.avif?t=1773777936\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928280/extras/2d4cd9f9d49ab83702c9a9908b5deb0f.webm?t=1773777936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928280/extras/2d4cd9f9d49ab83702c9a9908b5deb0f.mp4?t=1773777936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Got friends?</strong> Great! <strong>Crime is better together.</strong> Work as a team, complete insane objectives and share the chaos. <strong>Voice and text chat included.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No friends?</strong> No problem! Play offline and enjoy the destruction on your own.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every fight is a playground—<strong>cops, civilians, rival gangs</strong>—everyone is a target. Grab a baseball bat, throw a crowbar at full speed, or <strong>turn an enemy into a human fireworks show</strong>.</p>",
